parse.title: The Tolkien Art of the Brothers Hildebrandt 2005 Calendar

wikitext.*:
[[Image:The Tolkien Art of the Brothers Hildebrandt 2005 Calendar.jpg|thumb]]

'''The Tolkien Art of the Brothers Hildebrandt 2005 Calendar''' was produced by Entertainment Calendar, LLC and contains sketches and photos by the [[Brothers Hildebrandt]] which were saved from 1979.

* ISBN 1-58774-055-9
* Dimensions: 12 x 12 inches
* Stapled
* Punched hanging hole
* Shrink-wrapped
